- content_for :head do
  %title Crossroads Summer Block Party - Kansas City, Missouri
/ .divider
.main-content
  .row
    .content-header
      %h1.mega Howdy Neighbors!
      .grid
        .col
          %em
            We love KC bands and artists! That's why we don't want them to get electrocuted.
            Due to probable inclimate weather, we're moving the party to July 3rd!
          :markdown

            Join us July 3rd for the Crossroads Summer Block Party presented by [Golden Sound Records](https://goldensoundrecords.com) and [The Pitch](http://www.pitch.com)! Enjoy an evening of [live music](#schedule) from some of the best bands in town, tasty brews, curated art, and friendly neighbors.

            Bring your friends &amp; family to the First Fridays event of 2015 and discover a taste of what makes Kansas City and the Crossroads Arts District one-of-a-kind.
        .col.center= image_tag 'ill/flamingo.svg', id: 'flamingo_main'

      %p
        %a.sampler-download{href: "/sampler#main"}
          %i.icon-music
          Check out the Crossroads Summer Block Party 2015 Music Sampler
          %i.icon-music
      %p
        %a.button{href: "http://vip.crossroadsblockparty.com"} Interested in being a part of Crossroads Summer Block Party?
